>\r\n	<li>Help in localization of TradeHero</li>\r\n	<li>Help in launching of TradeHero onto Android and other platforms</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Skills Required:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Development on mobile applications across Android and iOS, key skillsets are Java and Objective C./ Server infrastructure running on Microsoft C# and SQL Server</li>\r\n	<li>Web development in HTML5/CSS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><i></i> Marketing Professional</h2>\r\n<strong>Qualifications:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellent command of English</li>\r\n	<li>Minimum tertiary level student or graduate in any subject</li>\r\n	<li>Must have permit to work in Singapore</li>\r\n	<li>Odd hours acceptable, such as 1-2 workday week, as long as commitment to work excellence is demonstrated</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Your responsibilities:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online marketing (Social media, PPC, mobile marketing, email marketing)</li>\r\n	<li>Market research (secondary research, surveys)</li>\r\n	<li>Creative ideas generation on a budget</li>\r\n	<li>PR (press lists/media contacts)</li>\r\n	<li>Other tasks as assigned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><i></i> Front-end / UI Designer</h2>\r\n<strong>Skills Required:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Front-end Web Development in HTML5/CSS</li>\r\n	<li>Wireframe and mockup designing skills using Photoshop</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent graphic design ablilities</li>\r\n	<li>Competent with Javascript/jQuery</li>\r\n	<li>Strong knowledge in frontend frameworks (Twitter bootstrap, Zurb Foundation, etc)</li>\r\n	<li>Familiarity with MVC, Git and any CMS are a plus</li>\r\n</ul>','Careers','','inherit','closed','open','','13-revision-2','','','2013-06-13 16:01:23','2013-06-13 08:01:23','',13,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=126',0,'revision','',0),(50,2,'2013-05-14 05:19:39','2013-05-14 05:19:39','<style><!--\r\nimg { border: 0px !important; } img.alignleft { margin:0px; }\r\n--></style><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://trade