d page to view cash balance and followers. Make more trades, gather more followers, and earn more!','How do I earn money from followers?','','publish','closed','open','','how-do-i-earn-money-from-followers','','','2013-06-13 17:06:30','2013-06-13 09:06:30','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?post_type=question&#038;p=117',0,'question','',0),(118,1,'2013-06-13 17:07:03','2013-06-13 09:07:03','The Return on Investment (“ROI”) is the most important value to track. It’s used to calculate your position on the global leaderboards. It is the percentage increase in the value of the stocks you have purchased. Keeping a consistently positive ROI is the best way to gather a huge amount of followers!\r\n\r\nROI = (Gain from Investment - Cost of Investment) / Cost of Investment * 100\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n<i>You invest $1000 to buy 2 different stocks\r\n1 month later, the value of your investment goes up by $100 to $1100\r\nYour ROI will for the 1 month duration is: ($1100 - $1000) / $1000 *100 = 10%</i>','What is ROI?','','publish','closed','closed','','what-is-roi','','','2013-06-13 17:15:01','2013-06-13 09:15:01','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?post_type=question&#038;p=118',0,'question','',0),(119,1,'2013-06-13 17:04:08','2013-06-13 09:04:08','[faq]','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','closed','open','','12-revision-4','','','2013-06-13 17:04:08','2013-06-13 09:04:08','',12,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=119',0,'revision','',0),(120,1,'2013-06-13 17:12:16','2013-06-13 09:12:16','[faq faq_topic=\"general\']\r\n\r\n[faq faq_topic=\"trading-terminologies\']','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','closed','open','','12-revision-5','','','2013-06-13 17:12:16','2013-06-13 09:12:16','',12,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=120',0,'revision','',0),(13,2,'2013-05-10 06:22:34','2013-05-10 06:22:34','Job posts','Careers','','publish','closed','closed','','careers','','','2013-06-13 17:38:32','2013-06-13 09:38:32','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(14,2,'2013-05-10 06:23:37','2013-05-10 06:23:37','<div>\n<h1>Join the team at TradeHero!</h1>\nIn between trips to the pub for <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delirium_Tremens_(beer)\">Delirium Tremens</a>, intense games of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Settlers_of_Catan\">Settlers of Catan</a>, battles in the meeting room and rounds of FIFA on the PS3, we manage to create <strong>the best Social Investment Network in the world!</strong>\n\nWe are looking for excellent individuals with an entrepreneurial mindset and an obsession with perfection. Warning: Working with Top-Table colleagues is extremely demanding, make sure you bring your A-Game!\n\n<a href=\"mailto:hiring@tradehero.mobi?subject=I%20want%20to%20join%20TradeHero!\"><strong>Join Us! »</strong></a>\n\n</div>\n<strong>What to expect:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Chance to work with excellent multi-national team with decades of investment banking, entrepreneurial, development and marketing experience</li>\n	<li>Opportunity to learn a diverse range of skills and gain invaluable experience</li>\n	<li>Highly agile and fast-paced environment</li>\n	<li>Short-term internships and full-time positions available</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><i></i> iOS/Android Developer</h2>\n<strong>Objectives:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Help in long term development of TradeHero</li>\n	<li>Help in development of TradeHero pivot points</li>\n	<li>Maintain TradeHero app and website</li>\n	<li>Help in localization of TradeHero</li>\n	<li>Help in launching of TradeHero onto Android and other platforms</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Skills Required:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Development on mobile applications across Android and iOS, key skillsets are Java and Objective C./ Server infrastructure running on Microsoft C# and SQL Server</li>\n	<li>Web development in HTML5/CSS</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><i></i> Marketing Professional</h2>\n<strong>Qualifications:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Excellent command of English</li>\n	<li>Minimum tertiary level student or graduate in any subject</li>\n	<li>Must have permit to work in Singapore</li>\n	<li>Odd hours acceptable, such as 1-2 workday week, as long as commitment to work excellence is demonstrated</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Your responsibilities:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Online marketing (Social media, PPC, mobile marketing, email marketing)</li>\n	<li>Market research (secondary research, surveys)</li>\n	<li>Creative ideas generation on a budget</li>\n	<li>PR (press lists/media contacts)</li>\n	<li>Other tasks as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2><i></i> Front-end / UI Designer</h2>\n<strong>Skills Required:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Front-end Web Development in HTML5/CSS</li>\n	<li>Wireframe and mockup designing skills using Photoshop</li>\n	<li>Excellent graphic design ablilities</li>\n	<li>Competent with Javascript/jQuery</li>\n	<li>Strong knowledge in frontend frameworks (Twitter bootstrap, Zurb Foundation, etc)</li>\n	<li>Familiarity with MVC, Git and any CMS are a plus</li>\n</ul>','Careers','','inherit','open','open','','13-autosave','','','2013-05-10 06:23:37','2013-05-10 06:23:37','',13,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/2013/05/13-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(15,2,'2013-05-10 06:32:17','2013-05-10 06:32:17','<style><!--\r\nimg { border: 0px !important; } img.alignleft { margin:0px; } .appstore-btn { display: block; background: url(http://tradehero.mobi/WebClient/img/appstore-small.png) no-repeat; background-position-y: top; margin: 0 auto; height: 48px; width: 163px; } .download { border-radius: 8px; float: left; padding: 4px; background: #FEFFFF; background: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #FEFFFF 0%, #D2EBF9 100%); background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0%,#FEFFFF), color-stop(100%,#D2EBF9)); background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #FEFFFF 0%,#D2EBF9 100%); background: -o-linear-gradient(top, #FEFFFF 0%,#D2EBF9 100%); background: -ms-linear-gradient(top, #FEFFFF 0%,#D2EBF9 100%); background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #FEFFFF 0%,#D