ilto:support@tradehero.mobi\">support@tradehero.mobi</a>).\r\n\r\nThat said, if you have some improvements in mind, feel free to contact us as well. We’ve received some great feedback along the way that has helped us tremendously. We know that some of you have asked us to include your local stock exchanges (Mexico and India, we hear you!) Don’t worry; we’re on it. We’re excited about the release of our Android version too!\r\n\r\nBehind every Trade Hero are the unsung heroes, the team from Singapore that has been working tirelessly to bring you this application. Our team in Singapore has largely expanded from 2 in early 2012, comprising Dinesh (our CEO) and Dominic (our CTO), to nearly 10 people now.\r\n\r\nPeter Lynch once said, “Owning stocks is like having children - don\'t get involved with more than you can handle.”\r\n\r\nTradeHero has, hopefully, come to the rescue.\r\n\r\nThat’s all for now – stay tuned for updates!','Welcome to TradeHero’s Official Blog ','','inherit','closed','open','','86-revision-4','','','2013-06-14 12:34:29','2013-06-14 04:34:29','',86,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=153',0,'revision','',0),(152,4,'2013-06-13 16:40:06','2013-06-13 08:40:06','Hey there,\r\n\r\nToday marks the 6th month since our launch on the 12<sup>th</sup> of December, 2012!\r\n\r\nOn this blog, we’ll be posting updates, stock market news &amp; tips, articles, information on TradeHero and much more. Check it out regularly for the latest news.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe’ve had an incredible 6 months. TradeHero’s up for its 2<sup>nd</sup> round of seed funding. Investors have generously responded and we’re on the right track. We’ve been contacted by people from all over the globe telling us that they love this app. If you’ve enjoyed our app so far, rate it on the App Store or let us know on Facebook (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/TradeHero\">www.facebook.com/TradeHero</a>), Twitter (@TradeHeroMobile) or email us (<a href=\"mailto:support@tradehero.mobi\">support@tradehero.mobi</a>).\r\n\r\nThat said, if you have some improvements in mind, feel free to contact us as well. We’ve received some great feedback along the way that has helped us tremendously. We know that some of you have asked us to include your local stock exchanges (Mexico and India, we hear you!) Don’t worry; we’re on it. We’re excited about the release of our Android version too.\r\n\r\nBehind every Trade Hero are the unsung heroes, the team from Singapore that has been working tirelessly to bring you this app. Our team in Singapore has expanded from 2 in early 2012, comprising Dinesh (our CEO) and Dominic (our CTO), to nearly 10 people. You’ll hear more about our team in the next couple of weeks.\r\n\r\nPeter Lynch once said, “Owning stocks is like having children - don\'t get involved with more than you can handle.”\r\n\r\nTradeHero has, hopefully, come to the rescue.\r\n\r\nThat’s all for now – stay tuned for updates!','Welcome to TradeHero’s Official Blog ','','inherit','closed','open','','86-revision-3','','','2013-06-13 16:40:06','2013-06-13 08:40:06','',86,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=152',0,'revision','',0),(154,4,'2013-06-15 21:00:15','2013-06-15 13:00:15','<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" alt=\"top10\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"250\" /></a>\r\n\r\nYet another achievement unlocked! TradeHero represented Singapore in the Echelon 2013 Tech Conference Asia held recently on the 4<sup>th</sup> and 5<sup>th</sup> of June at the Singapore Expo.\r\n\r\nWe also emerged as winners alongside iCarsClub at Echelon Satellite Singapore held 2 months before the actual conference.\r\n\r\nTradeHero has indeed come a long way.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe first joined the pitching at <strong>Echelon Satellite Singapore</strong> alongside 19 other startups, hoping to qualify to the finals. Emerging as winners together with iCarsClub, we were chosen to represent Singapore in Echelon 2013.\r\n\r\nWe pitched at the conference to over 2,000 entrepreneurs and investors.\r\n\r\nCheck out our pitch at Echelon 2013 done by our CEO, Dinesh here: <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8A6b3tnF49Y\">Pitch at Echelon (TradeHero)</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-2013-06-14-at-2.51.09-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-156\" alt=\"Pitching at Echelon 2013\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-2013-06-14-at-2.51.09-PM.png\" width=\"599\" height=\"594\" /></a>\r\n<i>Dinesh pitching at the conference (above) </i>\r\n\r\nDinesh was also interviewed during the conference. Do check out his interview here: <a href=\"https://www.vimily.com/share/wiJtT6ZjczX\">Interview with Dinesh</a>\r\n\r\nThe TradeHero team would like to thank Echelon 2013 for giving us this opportunity. We will continue working towards greater achievements to bring an even better Hero experience for everyone. Visit our main website at <a href=\"http://tradehero.mobi\">TradeHero-Home</a>! Stay tuned!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>The 10 pitching companies at Echelon 2013</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Echelon-2013-pitching-startups.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-168\" alt=\"Echelon-2013-pitching-startups\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Echelon-2013-pitching-startups.png\" width=\"560\" height=\"412\" /></a></p>\r\n<em>A little information about <strong>Echelon</strong>:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Echelon is a major Asian tech startup conference that gathers the best regional startups held annually. This year, Singapore had the privilege in hosting the event.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Over 100 companies around Asia pitched at the 9 satellites that were held, and 10 finalists were shortlisted by their professional team.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>For 