y/</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n“TradeHero is easy for anyone to participate and accessible on-the-go with your phone.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><strong>Marubozu</strong>: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">http://mystocksinvesting.com/trade-hero/follow-my-trades-at-tradehero-marubozu1688/</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nFollow his portfolio on TradeHero for the “exact trade detail on the entry price, exit price and stop loss”.\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Kiss Investing</strong>: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">http://kissinvesting.blogspot.sg/2013/02/tradehero-review-stock-market-app.html</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n“The <b><i>unique thing</i></b> about this App is that it combines both social networking and trading &amp; Good Traders can earn money from this!”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe’ve received some great suggestions from them. Thanks to BigFatPurse, we’ve noticed that certain traders have been investing heavily in sub-penny stocks. Also, as James Yeo of KISS Investing pointed out, top traders are currently ranked only by ROI.  In next version, traders will be ranked by their skill – we have developed a special algorithm to determine this.\r\n\r\nLike how TradeHero sounds? Try it out for yourself! You can download it from the App Store here (<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?ls=1&amp;mt=8\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tradehero-mobile/id572226383?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a>).\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Blog Reviews','','inherit','closed','open','','130-revision-9','','','2013-06-14 12:02:04','2013-06-14 04:02:04','',130,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=177',0,'revision','',0),(281,4,'2013-06-20 11:56:10','2013-06-20 03:56:10','<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" alt=\"top10\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"250\" /></a>\r\n\r\nYet another achievement unlocked! TradeHero represented Singapore